node_modules/
.env*.local

# Scan output — regenerated by `deepsec scan` / `process`. INFO.md
# and SETUP.md (manually edited) stay tracked. tech.json is auto-detected
# and stamps an absolute `rootPath` (one machine's home) on every scan, so it
# stays local like project.json rather than committing a per-machine path.
data/*/files/
data/*/runs/
data/*/reports/
data/*/project.json
data/*/tech.json
